reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was surprised how nice these were. Very cute details and even glass eyes. I didn’t know they were jointed, so that was a very pleasant surprise. The elbow joints only worked on one doll, but the knees on all worked. The hands and shoulders move as well. Very nice and cute.

reviews.reviewText: They are very cute and of great quality at a super low price. Excellent for giving as a gift and decorating. Recommended for children aged 5 and over.
